title: When I receive the issues of the project
content:
This is the D-Day, the list of issues are going to be revealed, how do you feel?

Quite confident, we've done a great job!

I remind that your current record is only 6 issues opened by the client!

Hum, not sure to beat it now, I have some doubts... Let's bet 10 issues, maximum 15...

Well, let's find out NOW!

And the client has opened no less than 1236 issues!

Unfortunately, it's a little bit more than expected.
